Let \( x=\frac{1}{t} \), so that \( dx=-\frac{dt}{t^2} \); then
\[
\int_0^\infty \frac{dx}{(1+x^2)(1+x^a)}
=\int_\infty^0 \frac{-\frac{dt}{t^2}}{\left(1+\frac{1}{t^2}\right)\left(1+\frac{1}{t^a}\right)}
=\int_0^\infty \frac{t^a\,dt}{(1+t^2)(1+t^a)}.
\]

